name: Openstreetmap Geofabrik, Belgium Points of Interest, Belgium , 2008
description: This open street maps data layer shows various points of interest throughout the country of Belgium. Points include post offices, hospitals, places of worship, parking, fuel, speed cameras, camp sites, schools, fire stations, courthouses, and so on. many of the attributes also have names associated with these points of interest.
